quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  3,84,"Boola mbu, “Khusuubile Nyasaye nende akeshibwa khu Ibrahim nende ka Musa yahelesibwa, nende Isa, nende Abarumwa okhurula khu Nyasaye wabu, Omulesi, shikhukabukhasinjiakhwo hakari wabu tawe, nafu khwilekhulile khuye.”"
  3,85,"Ne ukhaaba idini ilali yobwisilamu tawe, shalichamilwa tawe, ne ye mwikulu aliba mubandu basikha."
  3,86,"Nyasaye anyala okhulunjisia arie Abandu bakhaya olunyuma lwa okhusuubila khwabu, ne mana nibaba abaloli mbu Omurumwa uno niwobwatoto, mana ebifune bia habulafu nibiboolela? Ne Nyasaye shalunjisinjia Abandu abamabii tawe."
  3,87,"Abo omurungo kwabu ni mbu bali nende eshilaamo shia Nyasaye, nende shia Abamalaika nende eshia abandu boosi."
  3,88,"Balimenyamwo tsinyanga tsioosi, shibalitutuyilibwa eshinyasio tawe, ne shibalihebwa obwiyangu tawe."
  3,89,"Halali balia basaba eshileshelo olunyuma lwa ako, mana nibaba abalayi, toto Nyasaye Niwobulesheli muno, Owetsimbabaasi."
  3,90,"Toto balia bakhaya nibamalile okhusuubila, mana nibameta okhukhaya, shibalileshelwa tawe, ne abo nibo abandu abakora."
  3,91,"Toto balia bakhaya mana nibafwa nibali abakhayi, shibalichamilwa tawe kata nibarusia idhahabu eshialo eshilaamba okhubanunula. Abo balinyoola eshinyasio eshilulu, ne shibaliba nende ababahabina tawe."